Package: metrics-monitor-system
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: CVEDIX <support@cvedix.com>
Installed-Size: 2153
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34), libgcc-s1 (>= 3.3.1), libstdc++6 (>= 12)
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/cvedix/metrics_monitor_system
Description: Metrics Monitor System - Hardware Information API Server
 A REST API server that provides system hardware information using hwinfo library.
 Provides endpoints for system information, status, and device registration.
 .
 Features:
  - GET /v1/core/system/info - System hardware information
  - GET /v1/core/system/status - System status and metrics
  - POST /v1/core/system/info - Device registration (with Basic Auth)
  - POST /v1/core/system/reboot - System reboot
